Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毛裏，你想要別人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mauri, you want someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在還沒準備好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm not up for it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,起來吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Get up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,工作在埃爾帕索。你是那裏人，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Job's in El Paso. You're from there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又一個拒絕的理由。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Another reason to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告訴你，我要出去。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm trying to tell you, I'm getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,需要其他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來杯冰茶，謝謝。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Uh, an iced tea, {\i1}por favor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他媽的?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝醉了嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，只是累了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}U... uh, no, no, just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯。我需要你幫忙。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex. I need you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞭解這個城市。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它是太多了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是兩個人的工作。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The job is for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你在埃爾帕索不是有個兄弟嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Don't you have a brother in El Paso?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,毛裏……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mauri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在監視我嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Are you spying on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的工作就是瞭解情況，亞歷克斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's our job to know things, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以別再提退休的事了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So stop talking this retirement shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這樣的人是不會退休的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Men like us don't retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,馬歇爾先生，您的行李都準備好了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Here you go Mr. Marshall, you're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Anything else I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,馬歇爾先生?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mr. Marshall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，謝謝。我很好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, no, thank you. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,請再說一遍房間號碼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The room number again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,11-0-6。在鑰匙架上。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}11-0-6. It's on the key holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊,是的。謝謝你！\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ah, yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,請伏特加馬提尼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Vodka Martini, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,現在喝酒太早了嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So, too early in the day for a glass of wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說喝血腥瑪麗太晚了?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Or too late for a Bloody Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那要看今天是什麼樣的日子了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Guess that depends on what kind of day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想擁有的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}you wanna have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這取決於你，不是嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's up to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你獨自嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是現在。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快嗎?-我們繼續吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Pleasant trip? - Let's get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他在這裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Uh, yes, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起來和你想的一樣。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He looks like what you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他會沒事的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm sure he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧。現在再見。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alright. Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人說很快就能搞定。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Your people said this will be done quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它會。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要更具體的說法。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm gonna need a little more specificity than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不,你不會的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的越少越好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The less you know, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你.....推他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想救他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I was trying to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個騙子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You are a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,碧翠絲，你的遭遇。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, Beatriz, what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸做的事是不對的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What Papa did, it ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的錯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Now, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-孩子不應該接受治療-爸爸說…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- No child should be treated... - Papa said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「這是你如何花錢獲得免費。」\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}"It is how you pay to be free."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那裏比這裏好多了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It was better than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-我給你帶了這個。-我不要!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- I brought you these. - I don't want them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，有，呃，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen, there is, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,特別簽證…像你這樣的人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}a special visa for... people like you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,留在美國，而我們在做你的…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to stay in the US, while we're working on your...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓我說出來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You want me to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把你關在這裏是不對的\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's wrong that you're locked up here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而傷害你的人還在外面。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}while the men who did things to you are out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸說永遠不要說。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Papa said to never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你調走\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm gonna have you transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,給兒童保護機構，好嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to Child Protective Services, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會把你送去教養院。不是把你關起來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They'll put you in a group home. Not lock you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現在，我不期待任何回報。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Now, I don't expect anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，你想說就說吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay, if you wanna talk, you can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想，你可以不做。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If you don't wanna, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該生活得比這更好 碧翠絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看來今晚我要一個人了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Looks like I'm going solo tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把這個做完。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I gotta get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在市中心申請許可證。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I've got a permit filing downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,市中心嗎?-是的，我工作，溫迪。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Downtown? - Yeah, I work, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,合同不會直接跳上船。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Contracts don't just jump in the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用等我了。艾利斯?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Don't wait up for me. - Ellis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?-她的香水真他媽的臭。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Yeah? - Her perfume fucking stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,回家前把它洗掉，好嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Wash it off before you come home, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,狗屎!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請!-你知道我為什麼來這裏!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Please! - You know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這，這都是誤會。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's... it's all a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這總是一個誤會。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's always a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先生。請! 在哪裏?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- M... Please! - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在，在保險箱裏。樓上。拜託!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's... it's in the safe. Upstairs. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣做!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有，我什麼都沒說，好嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}[gasps] I didn't, I didn't say anything, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,事情本不該發展到這一步的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It wasn't, it wasn't supposed to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我在這裏，那就太過分了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If I'm here, it's gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裏，好的!好吧!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's here, alright! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的。打開它!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Okay. - Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,我只是……好吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alright, I just... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，如果我把它給你\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, if I give it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,加油!好的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Come on! - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，爸爸?你回家嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, Dad? You home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去安娜貝爾家。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm going over to Annabelle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能會在這過夜，好嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll probably stay over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只是讓你知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just letting you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你想晚點再做。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Maybe you want to do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,我是多任務。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Uh-huh, I'm multi-tasking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我只是不想今天就死。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, well I just don't wanna die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在德州怎麼可能不說西班牙語?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}How can you live in Texas and not speak Spanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的貓頭鷹!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Fucking owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨,丹尼。他在哪裏?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey, Danny. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,除了在我的犯罪現場亂踩?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Besides stomping all over my crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉探員，阿米斯特丹探員，這是范·坎普太太。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Agent Serra, Agent Amistead, this is Mrs. Van Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,溫迪，我保證這兩個是我最好的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Wendy, I guarantee these are two of my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把你跟我說的告訴他們。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just tell them what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯是……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ellis was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一起搶劫。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It was a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,保險箱被打開了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The safe was opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你把這些告訴莫拉警探了嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And you've told this to Detective Mora?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒跟警察談過。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I haven't talked to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我先給傑拉爾德打了電話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I called Gerald first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是努斯本特別探員\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, I'm... I'm sure Special Agent Nussbaum
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了嗎，我們的人越多\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}has made it clear to you, the more people we have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我很早就在做這個…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}working on this early on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就越有可能破案。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the better our chances of solving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫莫拉警探來，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Uh, so, I'm gonna go get Detective Mora,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣你就不用重複你說過的話了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}just so you don't have to repeat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你想出來給她錄口供嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You wanna come outside and take her statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你老闆是想買還是已經買了?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}your boss trying to get some or is he already getting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯，莫拉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's real nice, Mora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把被害人的妻子性感化。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sexualizing the wife of a murder victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人找你們。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No one asked for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是空降進來的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He just parachuted in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全同意你的觀點。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, couldn't agree with you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的調查。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}This is your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但讓我們一起做這件事\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But let's just do this, together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我會讓努斯鮑姆不再煩你\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and then I'll get Nussbaum off your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要做什麼交易。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't need to cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能別老是這麼混蛋?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Can you just not be an asshole all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說"好"吧，丹尼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just say "yes", Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,丹尼。-好吧，我們走。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Yes, Danny. - Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,范·坎普太太，這位是丹尼·莫拉警探。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mrs. Van Camp, this is Detective Danny Mora.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人，請節哀順變。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sorry for your loss, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你最後一次見到活著的丈夫是什麼時候?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}When's the last time you saw your husband alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚……9點左右。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Last night... around 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去參加一個藝術開幕式。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I... I was going to an art opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和埃利斯是……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And Ellis was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他打算申請許可證。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was going to file permits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來你丈夫有外遇。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sounds like your husband had something on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為他是去見朋友了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I assumed that he was, um, meeting a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有她的號碼,  或者他的…-琳達。。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- You have her number, or his... - Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓塞拉探員繼續審問。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let's have Agent Serra continue the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以給你她的電話號碼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I can get you her number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你,女士。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.12,0:24:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你有任何生意往來\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You have any business dealings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.96,0:24:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不妙，你認識的人會想傷害他嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}that went bad, anyone you know might wanna hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，我。。。我不知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Uh, I... I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請幫幫我!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.54,0:24:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼跟艾米說?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What am I gonna say to Em?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.32,0:25:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要期望太多。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.95,0:25:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,當阿爾茨海默氏癥的發作如此突然\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}When the onset of Alzheimer's is this sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道它是怎麼開始的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know how it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.03,0:25:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,夥計。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.90,0:25:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是我，亞歷克斯，你弟弟。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's me, Alex, your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很不錯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.17,0:25:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜怎麼著?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,前幾天我發現了這個。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I found this the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,1969. 讓我想起了你。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}1969. Made me think of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.88,0:25:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得那一年嗎?嗯?草案?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You remember that year? Huh? The draft?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.35,0:25:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽和雄鹿。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The Suns and the Bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.05,0:25:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人在首輪選秀中並列。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Both tied for the First Round Pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.22,0:25:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,歸結到拋硬幣……鳳凰城的電話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Down to a coin flip... Phoenix calls heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.93,0:25:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,對，是反面。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, it was tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.16,0:25:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鹿隊得到了盧·阿爾辛多。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And the goddamn Bucks get Lew Alcindor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.57,0:26:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我不怎麼看籃球了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, I don't watch basketball much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.08,0:26:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不記得上次是什麼時候了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Can't say I remember the last time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.09,0:26:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的船長今天早上打電話來了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}My Captain called this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.26,0:26:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,顯然，我不再被需要了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Apparently, I'm no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.10,0:27:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，很高興大家都來了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Good, I'm glad everybody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…鑒於里昂爸爸的突襲事件\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So... in light of what happened with the Papa Leon raid
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.94,0:27:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,特遣隊正在重組。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the Task Force is being reorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.24,0:27:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,馬奎斯警探就要回墨西哥了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Detective Marquez will be heading back to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.51,0:27:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還沒說完，長官。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We're not done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,與墨西哥警方的合作\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Cooperation with the Mexican Police has...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.28,0:27:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們完了，塞拉，我已經花了三天時間了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We're done, Serra, I've spent the last three days
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到華盛頓的嘮叨，事實就是事實。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}getting an earful from Washington, facts are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.45,0:27:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一項影響廣泛的國際調查\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}This has been a wide reaching international investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.95,0:27:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而我們卻一無所獲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and we got nothing to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.72,0:27:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你有話要說嗎，馬奎斯?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You have something you wanna say, Marquez?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.32,0:27:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是沒事，先生。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's not nothing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.16,0:27:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在墨西哥有很多。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We've gotten plenty in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們一到美國，事情就…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But as soon as we come into the US, things get, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.30,0:27:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，也許是你在華盛頓的\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't know, maybe your ears in Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.43,0:27:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不想聽。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}just don't wanna hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.24,0:27:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很明顯他們對大魚的胃口很大\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's pretty obvious the appetite for big fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.54,0:27:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到邊界為止。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}ends at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.04,0:27:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡你的暗示，馬奎斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't like what you're insinuating, Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.34,0:27:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不認為我在暗示什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't think I was insinuating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.18,0:27:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,說得很直白。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Was saying it pretty flat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.58,0:27:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,雨果說得有道理，長官。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hugo has a point, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.32,0:27:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在美國的帕德羅特沒有任何進展。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We've never gotten anywhere with the US-based {\i1}Padrote.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.45,0:27:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有這種東西的話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If there even is such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.05,0:27:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,據說利昂爸爸是為有錢人服務的。白人男性。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The word was Papa Leon served rich men. White men.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.36,0:27:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"那個詞"就是你們這些人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}"The Word," is that what you people
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.02,0:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在華雷斯立案調查?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}build cases on in Juarez?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.46,0:28:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有里昂爸爸的錄像帶\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We have Papa Leon on tape
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.69,0:28:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吹噓他的客戶。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}bragging about his clientele.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你覺得這是針對你。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, I know you take this personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.46,0:28:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是井干了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But the well's gone dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不願相信有一隻白色的帕德羅特，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know you don't want to believe there's a white {\i1}Padrote,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但結束一個案子並不代表就能成功。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}but shutting down a case don't make it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.37,0:28:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-小心點，塞拉。-我們有目擊證人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Watch yourself, Serra. - We have a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.34,0:28:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所擁有的…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.04,0:28:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是被拘留的非法未成年人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}is an undocumented minor in detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.38,0:28:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在面對的是一個精神嚴重受損的，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What we have is a severely traumatized,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.35,0:28:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被拘留的未成年人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}undocumented minor in detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.45,0:28:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我們唯一有價值的證人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And she's the only valuable witness we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.35,0:28:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算什麼時候告訴我你提出\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}When were you gonna tell me you offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,碧翠絲·萊昂T-1簽證?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Beatriz Leon a T-1 visa?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我正要說到這個。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I was coming to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.69,0:28:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把交易通知我\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}To notify me of the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.72,0:28:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有權利做?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}you're not authorized to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.36,0:28:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在你沒有立案的案子裏找證人?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}With a witness in a case you haven't made?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想幫助比碧翠絲·里昂這樣的孩子\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I thought helping kids like Beatriz Leon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們工作的一部分。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}was part of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.36,0:28:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她的資格。專責小組結束了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- She's eligible. - The Task Force is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.13,0:28:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是直接來自華盛頓的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And that is straight from Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.34,0:28:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至於碧翠絲，我們可以對她進行T-1轉移到教養院，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}As for Beatriz, we can T-1 her and move her to a group home,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得專注於范·坎普謀殺案\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}but you need to focus on the Van Camp murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.51,0:28:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是埃爾帕索警局，每天都是。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's El Paso PD, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幫助碧翠絲這樣的孩子嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You want to help a kid like Beatriz?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在謀殺案上合作。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You play ball on the homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.62,0:29:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,好的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.52,0:29:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您,先生。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,科爾曼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Coleman, Howe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,本周你會有新的任務分配。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You'll have new duty assignments this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.23,0:29:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,馬奎斯警探，我代表局裏\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Detective Marquez, on behalf of the Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.13,0:29:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,還有美國，我感謝你們的付出。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and the United States, I thank you for your service.
