Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.58,0:39:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已經準備好畏罪自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.15,0:39:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼6?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Why six?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.89,0:39:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會想知道的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.16,0:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上,我做的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Actually, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.89,0:39:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我在華雷斯辦一個案子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I was working on a case in Juarez.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.16,0:39:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,死去的女孩。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The Dead Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.90,0:39:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下，那麼多女人消失了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Imagine, so many women disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.84,0:39:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能什麼都不做。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and you can't do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.27,0:39:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說每個人都有自己的號碼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They say everyone has their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.74,0:39:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對警察來說，他們只是數字。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}For the police they're all just numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.91,0:40:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,6?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.88,0:40:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,埃米莉安娜·曼特拉斯當時13歲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Emiliana Manteras was 13 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.22,0:40:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她辭去了在馬奎拉多拉的工作，然後消失了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Left her job at a Maquilladora and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.92,0:40:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就消失了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.42,0:40:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,四個月後，生了幾個孩子\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Four months later, a couple of kids
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.85,0:40:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在垃圾堆裏發現了她的屍體。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}found her body in a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.19,0:40:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她的母親，她的姐妹。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Her mother, her sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.29,0:40:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是強大的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They were strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把艾米麗安娜的照片貼在牆上\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They plastered Emiliana's photo on the walls
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.00,0:40:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,整個城市的總部。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}of headquarters in all the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.07,0:40:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,問題不在於沒人知道\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The problem wasn't that no one knew
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.50,0:40:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩怎麼了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}what happened to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每個人都知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Everyone knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.47,0:40:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米麗安娜和一個士兵上了一輛車。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Emiliana got into a car with a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.28,0:40:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,埃圖羅·龐蒂利亞。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Arturo Pontilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.98,0:40:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,龐蒂利亞喜歡和毒梟聚會。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Pontilla liked to party with the Narcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.48,0:40:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟著他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.81,0:40:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不動聲色地立案了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I built the case quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.95,0:40:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然龐蒂利亞是軍人，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But since Pontilla was military,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,起訴書必須先交給他的指揮官\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the indictment had to go to his commander first
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.79,0:40:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他們就把他轉到錫那羅亞去了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and they just fucking transfer him to Sinaloa.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,三周後，艾米麗安娜的母親\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Three weeks later, Emiliana's mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.03,0:40:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,姨媽和三個姐妹失蹤了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}aunt and three sisters disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.97,0:40:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把那些女人吊死在橋上\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They hung those women from a bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.97,0:40:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我辦公室的窗前。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}right in front of my office window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.04,0:40:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.27,0:41:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該讀讀聖經。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You should learn the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.47,0:41:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.14,0:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,噓!嘿!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Shh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.57,0:41:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.14,0:41:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.31,0:41:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瑪雅。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.38,0:41:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你在酒店。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.85,0:41:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,酒店?是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Hotel? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.28,0:41:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,做了個噩夢。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.52,0:41:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.00,0:42:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，也許下次你來的時候\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That was nice, maybe next time you're in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.20,0:42:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會回來了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I won't be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.47,0:42:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.14,0:42:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你好運!-也敬你。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Good luck then! - And to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.14,0:42:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一個13歲的女孩\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}A 13-year-old girl
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.55,0:42:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在日落高地被謀殺了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}has been murdered in Sunset Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.65,0:42:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,未成年人，碧翠絲·萊昂，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The minor, Beatriz Leon,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.15,0:42:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,最近被安置在教養院嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}had recently been relocated to a group home
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.62,0:42:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來自埃爾帕索拘留所\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}from an El Paso detention center.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.92,0:42:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,據埃爾帕索警方發言人稱，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}According to an El Paso police spokesman,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.02,0:42:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那個年輕女孩的謀殺案是…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the young girl's murder is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.36,0:43:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚在這兒嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Was I here last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.53,0:43:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。怎麼了?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yes. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.16,0:43:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得到的細節非常少……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We're getting very few details...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.03,0:43:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你確定?是的!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- You sure? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.03,0:43:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-我在這裏?是的!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- I was here? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.37,0:43:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一整夜?是的!住手，你受傷了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- All night? - Yes! Stop it, you're hurting...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.50,0:43:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-我整晚都在這裏?是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- I was here all night? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的。很小心。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen to me. Very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.11,0:43:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須馬上離開。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.51,0:43:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒來過，我們也沒見過面。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You were never here, we never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.24,0:43:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-你明白嗎?我明白了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Do you understand? - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.91,0:43:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了。對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I have to go. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.65,0:43:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你暫時別再來這家酒店了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You stay away from this hotel for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.65,0:43:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-很長時間!好的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- A long while! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.98,0:43:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-你聽到了嗎? 是的!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Do you hear me? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.45,0:43:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要替任何人開門。任何人!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Do not answer that door for anyone. Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.26,0:43:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,執行得很好，值得注意\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well executed, it is worth noting
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.27,0:43:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,對兒童的暴力，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}that violence against children,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.10,0:43:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是販毒集團的名片嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}is a calling card of the cartels
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.64,0:43:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,越過邊境。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.11,0:43:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當市長被要求發表評論時，他沒有得到任何回應。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Called on for comment, the Mayor had none.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.15,0:44:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!你忘了吃藥，忘了吃藥\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey! You forgot them, you forgot your pills...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.65,0:44:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,回來!回來!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.75,0:46:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候變弱了，亞歷克斯?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}When did you go soft, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.85,0:46:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就會殺了你的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They'll end you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.09,0:46:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,退休快樂,Maury !\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Happy retirement, Maury!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.69,0:46:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.37,0:46:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.18,0:46:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，你有一顆35歲的心。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Goodness, you got the heart of a 35-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.18,0:46:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,照這樣下去，你能活到130歲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}At this rate, you'll live to be 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.85,0:46:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你五百萬，把它變成135。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll give you five million to make it 135.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.26,0:46:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你答應了，我就炒了你。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If you said, "Yes," I'd fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.30,0:46:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果我答應了，我會希望你答應的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know if I said yes, I'd want you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.20,0:47:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我祖父是阿布魯澤人。他活到了104歲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}My grandfather is a Abruzzese. He lived to be 104.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?幸運的人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah? Lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.14,0:47:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,亞得裏亞海沿岸的所有地區，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know, that all region, along the Adriatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.44,0:47:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和日本沖繩，他們把這些稱為藍色區域。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and Okinawa, Japan, they call those blue zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.71,0:47:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,通常有\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Places that generally have
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.88,0:47:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,百歲老人的比例更高。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}a higher percentage of centenarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.88,0:47:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道,約瑟夫。但是為什麼呢?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm aware, Joseph. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.42,0:47:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,營養?空氣中缺乏污染物?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Nutrition? Lack of pollutants in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.52,0:47:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有理由衰老，衰老。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}There is no reason we have to age, to decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.46,0:47:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一些醫學專業人士可能會這麼說。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Some medical professionals might actually argue that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.33,0:47:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都可以被重新編程，修改。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Everything can be reprogrammed, modded.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.43,0:47:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼人類的健康不應該是一樣的呢?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Why shouldn't human health be the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.53,0:47:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DNA的一種算法。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}DNA's an algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.33,0:47:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，我不會告訴你怎麼花錢。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, I'm not gonna tell you how to spend your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是當它這麼多\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Especially when so much of it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.24,0:47:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最後在你的口袋裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}ends up in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.42,0:47:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你給我打電話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I appreciate you giving me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.26,0:48:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道這鎮上到底發生了什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't know what the fuck is going on in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.83,0:48:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對天發誓，這裏越來越像阿富汗了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Swear to God, it's getting more like Afghanistan every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.37,0:48:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們是誰?匹配集。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Who are they? - Matched set.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.77,0:48:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,簡和喬·多伊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Jane and Joe Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.27,0:48:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他坐在駕駛座上，被炸飛了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was in the driver's seat, blown the fuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她在後備箱裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She was in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,點32口徑的子彈擊中頸部\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}.32 caliber bullet to the neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.21,0:48:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,帶有抑制標記的外殼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}jacketed with suppressor markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.67,0:48:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我們從碧翠絲·萊昂身上撤資一樣。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Just like we pulled out of Beatriz Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.88,0:48:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,車主是大衛·馬歇爾。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Car's registered to a David Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.41,0:48:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在機場租的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Rented at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.95,0:48:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一個從聖地亞哥來的商人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Some expat businessman out of San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.55,0:48:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是車裏的屍體。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Probably the corpse in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.39,0:48:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在對他們倆進行牙齒測試。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We're running teeth on them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.35,0:48:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙喝得爛醉如泥。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay, this guy is drunk as a skunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.72,0:48:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他用一把點24口徑的槍開了三次。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He, uh, pulled a .24 three times over the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.43,0:48:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我需要你在走之前在報告上簽字。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So I need you to sign off on the report before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.29,0:48:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.40,0:48:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼?-在地板上找到的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- What's that? - Found them on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.97,0:48:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的數據庫裏沒有任何匹配，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It didn't match anything on our database,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,實驗室正在做化學測試。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}so the lab is running chem-test.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.97,0:48:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這是處方，可能會有幫助\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If that's a prescription, it might help...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.47,0:48:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,實驗室已經在研究了，我們可能沒那麼華麗，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The lab's on it, we might not be fancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.37,0:48:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特，但我們不傻。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Vincent, but we ain't dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.44,0:48:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我去VICAP查馬歇爾的名字，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll run the Marshall name through VICAP,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.98,0:48:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看看有沒有什麼發現。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}see if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.38,0:48:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我去給你做彈道測試\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll hit you up with the ballistics
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.67,0:48:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等他們一回來。藥片也是一樣。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}as soon as they come back. Same with the pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.40,0:48:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,謝謝。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}yes,thank
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.82,0:49:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.42,0:49:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩的事我很抱歉，夥計。這太糟糕了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sorry about the girl, man. It was fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.94,0:49:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我回不去了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I couldn't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.01,0:49:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,墨西哥人不再愛你了嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They don't love you in Mexico anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.65,0:49:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在徵求我留下的許可吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're not asking for my permission to stay, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.88,0:49:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-琳達說我必須這麼做-這樣的話\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Linda said I had to. - Oh, well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.38,0:49:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣，你知道她是什麼樣的人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Come on, you know what she's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.49,0:49:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.72,0:49:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人在乎那個女孩，文森特。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Nobody gives a fuck about that girl, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.86,0:49:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你，我和琳達。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Except you, me and Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.50,0:49:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到你和她做不到的事。你知道嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I can do things you and her can't. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.80,0:49:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一個關心的公民。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}As a concerned citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.97,0:49:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,從墨西哥嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}From Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.04,0:49:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，關切的墨西哥公民。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay, concerned Mexican citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.47,0:49:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有問題的調查\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}With questionable investigative
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.01,0:49:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在美國的權威。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}authority in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.98,0:50:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，努斯鮑姆肯定會同意的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, Nussbaum is really gonna go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.05,0:50:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他媽的努斯鮑姆。我不為他工作。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Fuck Nussbaum. I don't work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.75,0:52:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，我向你保證我沒有理由\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ellis: Look, I promise you I had no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.62,0:52:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你給我一個，否則什麼都別說。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to say anything unless you give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.99,0:52:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯，你現在做的事真是愚蠢至極。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What you're doing right now is incredibly stupid, Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.66,0:52:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I hope you understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.06,0:52:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我別無選擇。我不會被排除在外。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You've left me no choice. I won't be cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.16,0:52:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，沒必要搞得這麼難看。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, this doesn't have to be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.77,0:52:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,勒索已經夠醜陋的了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Blackmail is already ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.60,0:52:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看，所有的,范·坎普先生!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, all... Mr. Van Camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.07,0:52:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是在談判。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We are not negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經越過了一條沒有退路的線。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You've crossed a line from which there is no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.80,0:54:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來是點32口徑的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Looks like another .32 caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.30,0:54:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜它是改裝過的\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And I'm guessing it's also gonna be jacketed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.33,0:54:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,帶有抑製器標記。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}with suppressor markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.17,0:54:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我去和他妻子談談。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm gonna go talk to the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.17,0:54:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你在那裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}See you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.64,0:54:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為他是對的嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Do you think he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.24,0:54:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打賭。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'd put money on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.91,0:54:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問，這是個問題。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}This is a problem, no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.81,0:54:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是一個打手在清理垃圾。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Maybe a hitter cleaning up some shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.79,0:54:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我回頭再找你們。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll catch you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.79,0:54:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.90,0:54:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,據我所知，塞拉，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Last time I checked, Serra,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.30,0:54:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你在調查范·坎普的謀殺案。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}you were working the Van Camp murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.00,0:54:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,據我所知，先生，我為聯邦調查局工作。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Last time I checked, sir, I work for the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.00,0:54:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才看到的是雨果·馬奎斯嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Was that Hugo Marquez I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.73,0:54:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,聽……我覺得其中有聯繫\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen... I think there's a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.64,0:54:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,碧翠絲·萊昂，無名女屍之間的聯繫\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}between Beatriz Leon, the Jane Doe found
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.74,0:54:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在市中心一輛車的後備箱裏，還有這個人，威廉·博登。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}in the trunk of the car downtown and this guy, William Borden.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.11,0:54:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這是一件0.32的彈殼，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If this does turn out to be a jacket of .32,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.68,0:55:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有三個人可能是被同一把槍殺死的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}that's three people likely killed with the same weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.68,0:55:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，我明白，那個女孩。她在你的皮膚下面。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Look, I get it, the girl. She's under your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.08,0:55:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你有點癡迷於\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Maybe you're a little obsessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.22,0:55:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在做我的工作。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.35,0:55:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雨果認為這是職業殺手，用來報復。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hugo thinks it's a pro, settling scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.99,0:55:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們認為可能是柵欄那邊的擊球手。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We think it could be a hitter from across the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.22,0:55:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能肯定。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But you can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.83,0:55:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不能，但如果彈道吻合，還有\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We can't, but if the ballistics match, and there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.00,0:55:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是一個墨西哥殺手在鎮上亂竄\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}really is a Mexican killer tearing ass through town,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.96,0:55:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可能要趕在那之前。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}we might want to get ahead of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.66,0:55:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要馬奎斯\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And we're gonna need Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.64,0:55:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，做你該做的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alright, do what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.37,0:55:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要一天更新兩次。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But I want updates twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.24,0:55:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.71,0:55:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,實驗室剛查出那些藥的情況。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Lab just came back on those pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.95,0:55:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Diffadyl。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Diffadyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.05,0:55:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾茨海默氏癥的藥物。你的槍手開始失控了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alzheimer's drug. Your shooter is loosing his shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.85,0:55:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的。妻子在裏面嗎?-是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Okay. Is the wife inside? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.82,0:55:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的手從籠子裏拿開。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Keep your hands away from the cage on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.26,0:55:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道這是藥物還是純粹的瘋狂。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't know if it's medicine or just plain crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.36,0:55:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-要來旁聽嗎? 確定。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Wanna sit in on this? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.27,0:56:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,波登夫人，我是塞拉探員。我是馬奎斯警探。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mrs. Borden, I'm Agent Serra. This is Detective Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.17,0:56:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,對發生的事我很抱歉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm sorry for what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.14,0:56:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,波登:生活的一部分，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Borden: Part of life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.35,0:56:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他們說的……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's what they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.28,0:56:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還不太明白。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hasn't really sunk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.12,0:56:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,美國聯邦調查局之意。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hmm, FBI. Fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.92,0:56:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你也是特工嗎?-墨西哥聯絡員。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- You an agent, too? - Liaison from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.76,0:56:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,墨西哥和威廉有什麼關係?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What's Mexico have to do with William?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.76,0:56:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他討厭這個地方。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He hated the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.13,0:56:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們…希望能找到答案。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, that's what we're... hoping to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.43,0:56:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到什麼不尋常的地方了嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Have you noticed anything unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.40,0:56:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,發生在過去幾周\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}happen in the past few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.14,0:56:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫的行為發生了什麼變化?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}where your husband's behavior has changed at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.74,0:56:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾的行為二十年來都沒變。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Will's behavior hasn't changed in 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.38,0:56:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不。什麼都沒有。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.04,0:56:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-他做的是什麼法律? 房地產。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- What kind of law did he do? - Real Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.45,0:56:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉這麼問，波登夫人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sorry to ask this, Mrs. Borden.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.85,0:56:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道你丈夫有沒有\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But do you know if your husband had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.32,0:56:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和賣淫有關係嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}any ties to prostitution?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.92,0:56:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道。坐下來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I have no idea. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.12,0:56:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,帳單付賬?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Bill paying for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.33,0:56:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來不像他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Doesn't seem like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.80,0:56:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫認識埃利斯·范·坎普嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Did your husband know Ellis Van Camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.06,0:57:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道溫迪。我在同樣的場合見過她。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know Wendy. I see her at the same events.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.10,0:57:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏就是個大型雞尾酒會。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's all one big cocktail party up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.21,0:57:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡雞尾酒嗎，警探?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You like cocktails, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.14,0:57:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特?冰鎮喝嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Margaritas? Pina Coladas?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.48,0:57:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的幫助，波登夫人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Thanks for your help, Mrs. Borden.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.78,0:57:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要什麼，給我們打電話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If you need anything, just give us a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.96,0:57:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕她不能被打擾\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm afraid she can't be disturbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.26,0:57:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,別他媽開口。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Don't even fucking start.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.10,0:57:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一早上都在給你打電話。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I've been calling you all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.80,0:57:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,波登死了。有人執行他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Borden's dead. Someone executed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.50,0:57:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他找到了波登，那他就快了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And if he got to Borden, then he's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.77,0:57:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊,媽媽\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Jesus, mum...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.52,0:57:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉沃。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}{\i1}Bravo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.25,0:57:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你得離開埃爾帕索。立即。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You need to leave El Paso. Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.86,0:58:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,坐公司的飛機。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Take the company plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.26,0:58:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,明天晚上怎麼樣，都安排好了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What about tomorrow night, it's all been arranged...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.06,0:58:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.10,0:58:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,明天派對結束後，你就飛去日內瓦。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Tomorrow, after the party, you'll fly to Geneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.97,0:58:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,待在家裏做好準備\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Stay at the house and make arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.50,0:58:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你去戒毒所。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}for you to check into rehab there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.20,0:58:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,康復嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Rehab?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.41,0:58:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果事情和你有關\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If things connect to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.07,0:58:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有麻煩了，你得工作\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and we have a problem, you will be working
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.54,0:58:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的問題，這能為我們爭取時間\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}on your issues, which will buy us time
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.15,0:58:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄僱傭非常好的律師\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to quietly hire very good lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.88,0:58:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,除了……你需要幫助，蘭迪。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Besides... you need help, Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.26,0:58:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.39,0:58:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.29,0:58:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，寶貝。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know you are, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.86,0:58:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.07,0:58:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,完整的彈道報告出來了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Full ballistics came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.20,0:58:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死碧翠絲和車裏無名女屍的是同一把槍，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Same gun killed Beatriz and the Jane Doe in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.07,0:58:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是波登。兩支32口徑手槍，兩支槍。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}but not Borden. Two .32s, two shooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.04,0:58:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,交易,文森特·塞拉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Trafficking, Vincent Serra.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.51,0:58:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是你帶那個女孩去教養院的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're the one who took the girl to the group home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.45,0:58:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎?-你是誰?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Weren't you? - Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.92,0:59:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,馬歇爾。大衛·馬歇爾。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Marshall. David Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.39,0:59:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,開發和跟蹤。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Tap and trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.25,0:59:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大衛·馬歇爾在市中心燒了一輛車。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ah, David Marshall burned up a car downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.32,0:59:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你幹的嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Is that your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.53,0:59:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再替你做你的工作了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I can't keep doing your job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.30,0:59:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼工作?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What job is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.40,0:59:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,波登，范坎普。他們對孩子們做了什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Borden, Van Camp. What they did to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.60,0:59:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都沒做。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're not doing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.33,0:59:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說你殺了威廉·波登嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Are you saying you killed William Borden?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.47,0:59:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-埃利斯·范·坎普呢?是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- And Ellis Van Camp?  Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.14,0:59:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩呢?碧翠絲 萊昂。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And what about the girl? Beatriz Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.48,0:59:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是女孩。這是毛。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Not the girl. That was Mauricio.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.88,0:59:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,車裏的男人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The man in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.08,0:59:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你太慢了，沒法讓他們付出代價。他們太富有。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're too slow to make them pay. They're too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.95,0:59:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-誰太有錢了?律師，客戶。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Who's too rich? - The lawyer, the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.29,0:59:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,客戶是誰?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Who's the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.23,0:59:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識她嗎?誰?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}-  Did you know her? - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.90,0:59:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那個，那個女孩。碧翠絲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The... the... the girl. B... Beatriz.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.23,0:59:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小女孩。你在乎嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- A little. Did you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.37,0:59:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,15秒。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Fifteen seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.24,0:59:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然不相信。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.91,0:59:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想相信你是個好人，文森特。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I want to believe that you are a good man, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.94,1:00:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是壞人。已經很長時間了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm the bad man. Have been for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.05,1:00:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們必須受到懲罰。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But they have to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.65,1:00:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不能完成這個……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If I can't finish this...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.92,1:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}you have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.39,1:00:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他在樓下的公園裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's downstairs in the park.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.40,1:00:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，讓開!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.27,1:00:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.31,1:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他在耍我們。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's fucking with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.98,1:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是說我們太慢了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's just telling us we're way too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.12,1:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一個混蛋在剝削一個孩子\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We've got an asshole exploiting a kid
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.55,1:00:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要花多長時間才能把他送上法庭?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and how long is it taking us to bring him to trial?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.19,1:00:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,兩到三年，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Two to three years, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.56,1:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他們太有錢了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He said they're too rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.13,1:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在，我們在販賣人口的問題上遇到了挫折\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Now, we've been getting push back on the trafficking
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.00,1:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,前進的每一步。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}every step of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.70,1:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我覺得他，他要出去了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, I think he's, he's taking out
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.97,1:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,販毒者，我們不能。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the traffickers that we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.01,1:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,離開我們的麵包屑。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Leaving us breadcrumbs.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.61,1:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,證明一個觀點。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Proving a point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.73,1:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…馬奎斯探員。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well... Detective Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.46,1:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你監視我多久了?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}How long were you watching me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.20,1:01:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛到，波登夫人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I just got here, Mrs. Borden.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.17,1:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不應該讓大門開著。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You shouldn't leave the gate open.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.20,1:01:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,該發生的就會發生。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Whatever will be will be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.71,1:01:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在看著我…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And if you're watching over me...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.14,1:01:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好擔心的，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}nothing to worry about, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.48,1:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個游泳健將。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're a strong swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.48,1:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我身材不好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.29,1:01:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是92年奧運會的候補隊員。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I was an alternate for the '92 Olympic team.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.63,1:02:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我17歲。這是我一生中最美好的時光。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I was 17. Best time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.20,1:02:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到了96年，我失去了一秒鐘。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}By '96, I'd lost a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.70,1:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是它。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.21,1:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Done.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.71,1:02:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是麥片盒\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So instead of a Wheaties Box
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.21,1:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在洛杉磯有個時髦的丈夫\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and a dashing husband in LA,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.48,1:02:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最後我來到了這裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.48,1:02:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在德克薩斯州。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}In Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.78,1:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把那個杯子遞給我嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Could you pass me that glass?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.72,1:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,當然。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.76,1:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什麼，警探?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So, what do you want, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.66,1:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.80,1:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來給你打掃泳池的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm not here to clean your pool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.30,1:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是真正的警察，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You are not a real cop here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.64,1:02:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是為此而來的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.81,1:02:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?不逮捕我?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What? To not arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.47,1:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽你丈夫說過什麼嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Have you ever heard your husband talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.28,1:02:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一個叫大衛·馬歇爾的人?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}a man named David Marshall?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.81,1:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是來問我問題的\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You didn't come here to ask me questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.15,1:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是為了這個來的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I didn't come here for that either.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.22,1:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒插手威廉的事。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I stayed out of William's business.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.69,1:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Wives know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.69,1:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道這個名字\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I never knew the name,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.56,1:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我聽到他在講電話\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}but I heard him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.13,1:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他很緊張。他不想讓我聽到。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was nervous. He didn't want me to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.30,1:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他說的是一個來自墨西哥城的人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was talking about a man from Mexico City.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.84,1:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前怎麼不說?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Why didn't you say something before?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.47,1:03:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因為跟他說話的人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Because of who he was talking to.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.44,1:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦納·西爾曼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Davana Sealman.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.17,1:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才什麼都沒說。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's why I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.71,1:03:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他被利用了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was being used.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.35,1:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.65,1:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該去。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You should go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.85,1:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你,波登夫人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Thank you, {\i1}Senora{\i} Borden.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.49,1:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,別再回來了，馬奎斯警探。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Don't ever come back, Detective Marquez.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.69,1:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦納·西爾曼嗎?你確定嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Davana Sealman? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.16,1:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是她說的名字。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's the name she said.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.86,1:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,博登可能是她的律師之一。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Borden was probably one of her attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.20,1:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有，名單上沒有波登的名字\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Nope, Borden's name isn't listed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.17,1:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對海洋公司的任何申請\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}on any of the filings for Sea Corp
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.60,1:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,或達瓦納·西爾曼本人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}or Davana Sealman personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.44,1:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我們說的是最強大的\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You realize we're talking about one of the most powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.87,1:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,國內的房地產大亨，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}real estate moguls in the country, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.61,1:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.88,1:03:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，但博登和西爾曼通過電話\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know, but Borden spoke to Sealman on the phone
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.74,1:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,關於"來自墨西哥城的男人"\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}about the "Man from Mexico City."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.35,1:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你有證據嗎?那你至少上過她了吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, you got proof? Well, did you bang her at least?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.15,1:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說，如果你相信一個半醉的人的話\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I mean, if you're gonna take the word of a half-drunk
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.72,1:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,花瓶老婆，你也能從中得到點什麼，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}trophy wife, you may as well get something out of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.89,1:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-她詳細說明了嗎? 什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Did she elaborate? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.36,1:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,關於"來自墨西哥城的人"\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}On the "Man from Mexico City."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.76,1:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴，等等!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Shut up, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.36,1:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,波登不是達瓦納·西爾曼的律師。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Borden wasn't one of Davana Sealman's lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.23,1:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他是蘭迪·西爾曼的律師之一。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was one of Randy Sealman's lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.23,1:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦納的兒子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Davana's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.37,1:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,顯然，蘭迪也是個房地產大亨。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Apparently, Randy's also a real estate mogul.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.67,1:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,他媽的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.57,1:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭迪·西爾曼的公司擁有中央處理設施。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Randy Sealman's company owns the Central Processing facility.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.88,1:04:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把碧翠絲送去了那裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Where they sent Beatriz.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.35,1:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒注意到嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey, in case you haven't noticed,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.35,1:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他們派了很多人去那裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}they send a lot of people there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.78,1:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是的，我知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.92,1:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但她的13個。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But she's 13.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.22,1:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下在那個年紀你有多脆弱\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Imagine how vulnerable you feel at that age
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.52,1:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在ICE中心。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}in an ICE center.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.39,1:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，讓我們看看。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.36,1:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧。這不是她第一次去那裏了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay. Well, it's not her first time there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.23,1:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她去年在那裏待了三個星期\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She was there last year for three weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.57,1:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和她父親一起，然後他們被驅逐出境。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}with her father, and then they were deported.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.37,1:04:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,它變得棘手。埃利斯·范·坎普是CPF的建設者。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It gets stickier. Ellis Van Camp was CPF's builder.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.71,1:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所有和這個加工中心有關的人，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So everyone associated with this Processing Centre,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.41,1:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,律師，建築工人，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the lawyer, the builder,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.94,1:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,碧翠絲,都死了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Beatriz, all dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.95,1:05:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他會殺了蘭迪·西爾曼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's going to kill Randy Sealman.
