Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.35,1:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 來吧\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}♪ Come on ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.02,1:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喝值班嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Drinking on duty?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.62,1:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這離官方說法還遠著呢。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}This is so far away from official.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.76,1:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙,\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So this guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.39,1:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他是看守所的老闆。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}he owns the detention center.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.33,1:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道我們為什麼要保護他嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And you're wondering why we're protecting him?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.33,1:06:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一點也不奇怪為什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't wonder why at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.70,1:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 在深夜\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}♪ Deep in the night ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.81,1:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 在深夜\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}♪ Deep in the night ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.38,1:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿米斯特丹嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Amistead?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.64,1:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭迪在下層甲板，往裏面走。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Randy is on the lower deck, moving inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.51,1:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在路上。- 雨果，盯著甲板。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- On my way. - Hugo, keep eyes on deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.78,1:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.42,1:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,目標在船上!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Target's on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.81,1:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,把那玩意兒脫了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Take that shit off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.05,1:07:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我離開時，鎖上門。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}When I leave, lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.85,1:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧?好姑娘。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay? Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.73,1:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你人渣。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You scum.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.09,1:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,把它放下。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Put it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.96,1:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊!。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.60,1:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是文森特，對嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're Vincent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.03,1:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.50,1:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是亞歷克斯。亞歷克斯·劉易斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm Alex. Alex Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.07,1:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那些人對那孩子做了什麼，對吧?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know what those people did to that child, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.97,1:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Only too well.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.91,1:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我做過瘋狂的事情。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I've done crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.21,1:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但你永遠不會傷害孩子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But you don't hurt children, ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.48,1:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，為什麼我們不…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen, why don't you and I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.48,1:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-隻是談談?-沒時間了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Just have a talk? - No time for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.62,1:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你為什麼這麼說。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I understand why you're saying that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.05,1:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你身體不好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I know you're not well.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.92,1:09:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都得死，文森特。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We all have to die, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.52,1:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是你走之前要做什麼\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What's important is what you do before you go...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.12,1:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特!把槍放下!-滾出去，滾出去!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Vincent! Put your gun down! - Get outta here get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.53,1:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你朋友槍法好嗎?非常。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Is your friend a good shot? - Very.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.20,1:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-那就看你的了。不要動!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Then it's in your hands. - Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.93,1:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把他媽的槍放下!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Put the fucking gun down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.20,1:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我死了，她就不會知道真相了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If I'm dead, she'll never know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.80,1:09:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把槍放下。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Put the gun down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.36,1:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，嘿!-你他媽在幹什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Hey, hey, hey! - What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.83,1:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我15年前就戒酒了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know, I quit drinking 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.08,1:11:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在，我真的能嘗到威士忌的味道\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But right now, I can actually taste the scotch
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.08,1:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的喉嚨後面。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}in the back of my throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.18,1:11:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦娜·西爾曼唯一的兒子\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Davana Sealman's only son
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.68,1:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在我眼皮底下被殺了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}was just murdered on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.15,1:11:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她對我們不滿意。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She's not happy with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.65,1:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這位女士甚至僱傭了下班的警察來保護她。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The lady has even hired off-duty cops for protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.99,1:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他早在我們前面了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was way ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.66,1:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能在派對開始前就在船上了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He was probably on that boat before the party even began.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.33,1:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是誰，文斯?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Who is this fucking guy, Vince?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.26,1:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯·劉易斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.26,1:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以告訴你他是美國人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, I can tell you he's American.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.63,1:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他無疑是個承包商，但是…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's no doubt a contractor, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.67,1:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不認為這些都是命中的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't think these have all been hits.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.30,1:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他想為碧翠絲·里昂報仇。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He wants revenge for Beatriz Leon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.22,1:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先生,你還好嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sir, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.26,1:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚喝酒了嗎，先生?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Have you been drinking tonight, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.76,1:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,保羅……\Paul...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.36,1:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,保羅和他的兒子們。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Paul with his sons.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.18,1:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.85,1:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,摩托車巡警埃裏克·萊爾。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Motorcycle patrolman Eric Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.02,1:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是發現亞歷克斯受傷了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Must have found Alex wounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.02,1:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那輛野馬上全是血。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}There was blood all over the Bronco.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.05,1:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道。也許他被嚇到了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't know. Maybe he got spooked.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.86,1:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是他的風格。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That's not his style.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.29,1:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他的風格就是謀殺，文森特。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}His style is murder, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.56,1:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我們得在埃爾帕索警局之前找到他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, we need to find him before the El Paso PD.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.86,1:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不會高興的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They're not going to be happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.10,1:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道一些他們不知道的事。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, we know something they don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.43,1:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我知道亞歷克斯·劉易斯是誰了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I think I know who Alex Lewis is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.44,1:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,琳達:我查了青少年犯罪記錄。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Linda: I ran juvenile records.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.94,1:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,汽車偷竊,破壞攻擊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Vandalism, auto-theft, assault.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.34,1:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, it could be him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.98,1:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的問題是，亞歷克斯·劉易斯死了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Only problem is, Alex Lewis is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.18,1:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他和他父親在自家麵包店的火災中喪生\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He and his father died in the fire at the family bakery
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.41,1:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,四十年前。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}forty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.92,1:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,調查人員認為是亞歷克斯放的火。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Investigators thought Alex set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.95,1:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不過哥哥還在城裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Brother's still in town though.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.45,1:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,公園路上的護理中心。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Care facility on the parkway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.86,1:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,先進的阿爾茨海默氏癥。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Advanced Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.92,1:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,男人的一種蔬菜。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Man's a vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.99,1:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我還找到了醫療記錄。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I also came up with medical records.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.06,1:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯和他哥哥在急診室很有名。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex and his brother were well known at the ER.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.26,1:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,總是"從樓梯上摔下來"或"意外燒傷"\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Always a "fall down the stairs" or an "accidental burn."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.90,1:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其他事情則更難隱藏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Other things were harder to hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.34,1:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,父親從未被指控虐待。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Father was never charged with the abuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.44,1:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,性或物理。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sexual or physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.57,1:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要我搜查麵包店嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Want me to warrant the bakery?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.34,1:16:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.07,1:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個來自墨西哥城的傢伙，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}This guy from Mexico City,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.60,1:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是波登跟達瓦納·西爾曼說的那個。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the one Borden was talking to Davana Sealman about.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.44,1:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是她雇的呢?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What if she hired him?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.24,1:17:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我在想如果亞歷克斯沒醒來\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}'Cause I'm thinking if Alex is not up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.71,1:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到親手殺了西爾曼\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to killing Sealman himself,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.15,1:17:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他想讓我們把她帶回來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}he wants us to bring her in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.71,1:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,逮住唯一能連接的人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Catch is, the only person who can connect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.55,1:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和西爾曼的任何關係\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Sealman to any of this...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.65,1:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她比其他任何一個都更難接近。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She's harder to get to than any of the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.72,1:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他來找你是為了賠錢。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He reached out to you to cover his bets.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.72,1:18:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,保羅和亞歷克斯家唯一的地址\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The only address from Paul and Alex's
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.46,1:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,醫療記錄是麵包房。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}medical records is the bakery.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.73,1:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧，那地方一團糟。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, forget about it, that place is a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.13,1:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你在找一隻鴿子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Unless you're looking for a pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.33,1:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.77,1:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,鴿子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Pigeons.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.00,1:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,裏面塞上。這地方到處都是。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}{\i1}Palomas.{\i} The place is full of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.34,1:18:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那輛野馬的化驗報告…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The lab report on the Bronco...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.21,1:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那個巡警被殺的案子，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the one where the patrolman got killed,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.34,1:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地板上有鴿子糞便的痕跡。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}the floor had traces of pigeon shit on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.29,1:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能為你做點什麼嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Anything I can get you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.56,1:19:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.83,1:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Anything you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.86,1:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不了,謝謝。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.45,1:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到了，孩子們。檢查。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Top of the hour, boys. Check in.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.73,1:20:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老闆!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Boss!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.70,1:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他起來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.74,1:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,給他一個新電池。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Get him a new battery.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.95,1:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-把它們放下!現在!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Put them down! - Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.93,1:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你!回來!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.68,1:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在這裏。不要給任何人打開那扇門。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Stay in here. Don't open that door to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.22,1:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們!主要的辦公室。活射擊!活射擊!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Boys! Main office. Live shooter! Live shooter!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.87,1:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他往屋頂去了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's headed for the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.89,1:22:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,莫拉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mora.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.35,1:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,莫拉，他在屋頂上。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Mora, he's on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.69,1:23:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,副本。如果有機會，就把他幹掉。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Copy. If you get the chance, put him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.63,1:23:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.77,1:23:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都結束了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.90,1:23:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶你離開這裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let's get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.36,1:23:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你殺了我兒子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You killed my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.57,1:23:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.94,1:23:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做了什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And I know what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.60,1:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,撞針。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Firing pin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.58,1:24:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我剛才為什麼不幹掉你嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know why I didn't just off you back there?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.05,1:24:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我告訴你為什麼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let me tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.16,1:24:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是仁慈。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That would have been mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.80,1:24:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不。我想看你去尤馬。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No. I want to see you go to Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.97,1:24:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證他們會把你操死，老頭。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Where I will make sure they fuck you to death, old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.94,1:24:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個殺警察的混蛋。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You cop-killing piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.61,1:24:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個小女孩怎麼樣?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}How about that little girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.64,1:25:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他們會怎麼對待傷害孩子的人嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know what they do to people who hurt kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.55,1:25:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我會和FBI探員V- V-文森特·塞拉談談。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll talk to FBI Agent V... V... Vincent Serra.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.89,1:25:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其他人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No one else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.43,1:25:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他媽的聯邦調查局。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Fuck the feds.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.06,1:25:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們指控你三起謀殺。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We got you on three counts of murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.73,1:25:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的破槍和波登的匹配\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Your busted fucking gun matches Borden
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.03,1:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,還有埃裏克·萊爾警官。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and Officer Eric Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.53,1:25:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他有妻子和兩個孩子\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Guy had a wife and two kids...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.03,1:25:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼!他需要看醫生。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Danny! He needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.81,1:25:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不,他沒有。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.51,1:25:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一整天的時間，到最後，我對天發誓，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I've got all day, and by the end, I swear to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.78,1:25:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一份認罪書。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'll have me a written confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.92,1:25:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他拿著破槍去追西爾曼，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}If he went after Sealman with a broken gun,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.12,1:25:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會聽到一些聲音。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}we'd have heard something.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.86,1:25:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得他在最後。他什麼都不記得了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I just think he's at the end. He ain't remembering things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.72,1:25:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，產後抑鬱癥已經完全消失了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And also, PPD has gone totally silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.13,1:25:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這是麵包店的地址。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And this came from the bakery address.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.80,1:25:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它是什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.55,1:26:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,耶穌。你從哪兒弄來的?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Jesus. Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.69,1:26:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.19,1:26:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,埃爾帕索警局拘留了亞歷克斯·劉易斯\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}El Paso PD are holding Alex Lewis
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.02,1:26:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你把他移交給我們\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and I need you to transfer him into our custody.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.19,1:26:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他成為他們的問題。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let him be their problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.76,1:26:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想站在哪一邊?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Which side of this do you really want to be on?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.50,1:26:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我得跟他談談。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I need to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.77,1:26:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但它似乎是非常強大的人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But it seems very powerful people
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.57,1:26:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望這種事發生。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.64,1:27:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你他媽的對他做了什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}What the fuck did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.74,1:27:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-他拒捕。-所以你要拆散他?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- He resisted arrest. - So you had to bust him up?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.28,1:27:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是個警察殺手。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's a cop killer for fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.85,1:27:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡被達瓦納·西爾曼收買嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You like being on Davana Sealman's payroll?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.05,1:27:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.85,1:27:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來!\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Cool off!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.10,1:27:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,很好。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.90,1:27:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,美國聯邦調查局。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.90,1:27:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.07,1:27:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是你朝我開槍的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You are the one that shot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.91,1:27:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會道歉的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm not going to offer an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.64,1:27:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要你這麼做。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm not asking for one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.78,1:27:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你！\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.63,1:28:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這些藥撐不了多久了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}These aren't going to help for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.94,1:28:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想澄清這件事。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I understand you want to clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.27,1:28:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,弄清楚?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Clear this up?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.84,1:28:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.17,1:28:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要西爾曼死。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I want Sealman dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.91,1:28:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒有正式的犯罪記錄。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Well, she's not officially tied to any crime.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.11,1:28:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那不是真的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.08,1:28:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她批准了這次襲擊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She sanctioned the hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.95,1:28:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她雇我去殺…兩個人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She hired me to kill... two people.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.95,1:28:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯·范·坎普，第二個就是那個孩子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ellis Van Camp and the second was that child.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.86,1:28:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,十三歲的女孩。碧翠絲。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Girl of thirteen. Be... Be... Beatriz.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.33,1:28:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會那樣做的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.20,1:28:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.66,1:28:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不。你不能碰孩子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}No. You don't touch children.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.70,1:28:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，按下。謝謝。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Okay, press down. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.67,1:28:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很感激你在我身邊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I really appreciate you being here for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.24,1:28:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在這一切。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}During all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.21,1:28:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你不只是一個客戶。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're not just a client, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.41,1:28:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎，約瑟夫?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Is that true, Joseph?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.81,1:28:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，最難的事就是從不相信別人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know, the hardest thing is never really trusting
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.42,1:28:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那些和你親近的人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}those people close to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.42,1:29:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,除了蘭迪……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Besides Randy...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.99,1:29:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我永遠不會知道為什麼有人會和我在一起。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I will never really know why someone is with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.26,1:29:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧。我是你的朋友，達瓦娜。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Come on. I'm your friend, Davana.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.33,1:29:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在你身邊。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.40,1:29:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你的律師費是一千萬美元。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The retainer for your services is $10 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.44,1:29:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.84,1:29:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你在要求我做什麼嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Do you realize what you're asking me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.68,1:29:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉。不。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm sorry. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.41,1:29:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-我發過誓。起誓嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- I took an oath. - An oath?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.02,1:29:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就像結婚誓言?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Like a marriage vow?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.15,1:29:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了蘭迪的派對。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You were at Randy's parties.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.76,1:29:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我不知道嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You think I didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.69,1:29:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，讓我們簡單點。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So, let's make this simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.89,1:29:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,1000萬美元，否則起訴\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}$10 million or prosecution
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.70,1:29:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還因為與未成年人發生性關係而入獄。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and prison for sex with minors.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.46,1:29:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦納\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Davana...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.83,1:29:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要瞭解一些事情。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You need to understand something.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.43,1:29:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭迪是弱。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Randy was weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.10,1:29:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是我兒子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But he was my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.17,1:29:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.04,1:30:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雇兇殺人。謀殺報復。虐待兒童。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Vincent: Murder for hire. Murder for revenge. Child abuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.05,1:30:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都在這裏了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.08,1:30:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是結束。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.48,1:30:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每個人都死了,亞歷克斯。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Everybody's dead, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.79,1:30:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你上了庭，你也會被判終身監禁，朋友，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Even if you do make it to trial, you get life, my friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.96,1:30:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是醫生告訴我的嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}which from what the doctors tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.93,1:30:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大概三到六個月。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}is maybe three to six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.83,1:30:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，我們在這裏做什麼?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So, what are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.20,1:30:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們為什麼在這裏?Davana Sealman。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Why are we here? - Davana Sealman.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.10,1:30:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,正義。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Justice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.47,1:30:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正義嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Justice?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.80,1:30:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在開玩笑嗎?-我可以作證\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Are you kidding me? - I'll testify to all that...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.31,1:30:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個職業殺手。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You're a contract killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.01,1:30:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得你的證詞能在法庭上站得住腳嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You think your testimony's going to stand up in court?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.35,1:30:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-她雇我去殺一個孩子-你寫下來了嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- She hired me to kill a child. - Did you get that in writing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.02,1:30:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要那個證據。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We're gonna need that evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.49,1:30:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以為我們能伸張正義嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You really expect we're gonna find justice?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.22,1:30:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你試一試。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I expect you to try.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.96,1:30:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,聽……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.83,1:30:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我告訴你…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.36,1:30:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,關於正義。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}about justice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.20,1:30:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,12個月前,\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Twelve months ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.90,1:30:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一個醉駕的司機在8號州際公路上飛馳\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}a drunk driver was flying down the I-8
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.77,1:30:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在一輛偷來的車裏。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}in a stolen car.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.84,1:31:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他嗑藥嗑嗨了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's high on meth.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.84,1:31:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有看到另一輛車\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He hasn't seen another car
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.11,1:31:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是靠邊停車。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}that's pulled over on the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.48,1:31:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一位母親和她十歲的兒子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}A mom and her ten-year-old son.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.15,1:31:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,從樂高樂園回家。他們的輪胎漏氣了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Coming home from Legoland. They got a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.95,1:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是柯維，他沒看到那個女人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But Colvey, he doesn't see that the woman
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.48,1:31:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面換輪胎。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}is out there changing the tire.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.25,1:31:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他直接撞到她身上。殺死了她。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He just plows right into her. Kills her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.15,1:31:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在，他停下了車\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Now, he stops his car
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.92,1:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他看到他身後的男孩跳了出來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and he sees behind him the boy's jumped out.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.26,1:31:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他顯然尖叫。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He's obviously screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.86,1:31:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看到他媽媽，死在路上，哭喊著求救。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Seeing his mom, dead on the road, crying for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.36,1:31:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但柯維幫不上忙。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But Colvey doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.23,1:31:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他倒車，從男孩身上倒了過去。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}He puts his car in reverse and backs over the boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.54,1:31:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,確保沒有目擊證人\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Making sure there's no witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.27,1:31:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他在兩英里外的路上燒了車。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Then he torches his car two miles down the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.07,1:31:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一個15歲的女孩，看到了他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But a 15-year-old girl, she sees him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.38,1:31:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她看到一個男人拿著煤氣罐從大火中走出來。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She sees a man walking away from a big fire with a gas can.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.08,1:31:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不多，但已經足夠了\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Now, it ain't much, but it's enough
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.48,1:31:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,審判柯維\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}to put Colvey on trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.48,1:31:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道發生了什麼嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}You know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.39,1:31:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會照張相。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}They do a photo line-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.95,1:31:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但那女孩，她沒選柯維。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}But the girl, she doesn't pick Colvey.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.42,1:31:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他們會親自做，\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So they do an in-person,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.82,1:31:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她也沒有選柯維\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}and again she doesn't pick Colvey,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.56,1:31:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管大家都知道是他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}even though everybody knows it's him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.30,1:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,三次，排成三排。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Three times, three line-ups.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.90,1:32:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,每次她都選一個不同的男人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Each time she picks a different guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.17,1:32:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和柯維走。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And Colvey walks.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.03,1:32:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他還逍遙法外。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And he's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.57,1:32:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.41,1:32:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,記憶是一個混蛋。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}memory's a motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.91,1:32:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至於正義…\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}And as for justice...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.42,1:32:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它不保證。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}It ain't guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.05,1:32:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妻子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.06,1:32:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的兒子。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.24,1:32:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有證據。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I have evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.21,1:32:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?你有什麼證據?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah? What evidence do you got?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.91,1:32:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一個電話。達瓦納·西爾曼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}A phone call. Davana Sealman.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.95,1:32:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,威脅……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Threatening...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.15,1:32:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,威脅我殺的第一個人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Threatening the first man I killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.35,1:32:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯 范陣營呢?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Ellis Van Camp?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.96,1:33:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。我有個電話…翻轉……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yes. I have that call on a... flip...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.99,1:33:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快閃?Flash。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Flash? - Flash.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.23,1:33:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,閃存驅動器嗎?閃存驅動器。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Flash drive? - Flash drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.33,1:33:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裏?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.27,1:33:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.54,1:33:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,的幫助,幫我……\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Help, help me...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.47,1:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我記住。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Help me remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.58,1:33:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,請。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.41,1:33:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We will.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.15,1:33:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}We will.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.29,1:33:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓我感到噁心。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That makes me sick to my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.12,1:33:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興那個混蛋死了。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}I'm glad that bastard is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.52,1:33:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他母親在掩護他。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}His mother was covering for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.46,1:33:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,達瓦納·西爾曼嗎?是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}- Davana Sealman?  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.53,1:33:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人一輩子都沒開過停車罰單。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}That woman hasn't had a parking ticket in her life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.17,1:33:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道她的兒子在強姦未成年人。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She knew that her son was raping minors.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.37,1:33:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她還為埃利斯·范·坎普的死付了錢。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}She also paid for the hit on Ellis Van Camp.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.70,1:33:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,根據什麼證據?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Based on what evidence?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.44,1:33:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她雇的那個人，亞歷克斯·劉易斯。他跟我說得很清楚\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}The man she hired, Alex Lewis. He made it very clear to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.31,1:33:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,職業殺手的證詞嗎?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Oh, the testimony of a professional killer?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.58,1:33:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯·劉易斯受雇於威廉·波登\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Alex Lewis was hired by William Borden
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.65,1:33:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對於達瓦納·西爾曼。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}for Davana Sealman.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.98,1:33:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是同一個人嗎\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Isn't this the same man
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.98,1:33:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,誰得了癡呆?\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}who has some kind of dementia?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.08,1:33:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先進的阿爾茨海默氏癥。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Advanced Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.28,1:33:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,是的。\N{\c&H62A8EB&\fs13}Yeah, yeah.
